draft.title: SMARTYPANTS Halloween Witch Sweatshirt - Empress Tarot Card Jumper With Spooky 90s Movie Sister Design - Front And Back Print Pullover For Women - Mystical Divination Hocus Themed Novelty Gift
draft.description:
Embrace the magic of the spooky season with this unique Empress tarot card sweatshirt. Inspired by iconic 90s film witches, this jumper features a stunning back print of a beloved blonde enchantress, reimagined in a beautiful Art Nouveau style. A smaller matching design on the chest completes the mystical look.

Crafted from a premium cotton blend, this pullover offers the ultimate in comfort and warmth, making it your go-to choice for crisp autumn evenings or casual everyday wear. The high-quality fabric is soft against the skin and built to last.

Whether you're looking for the perfect gift for a fellow fan or treating yourself to some magical new apparel, this sweatshirt is a standout piece. It's ideal for Halloween parties, film marathons, or simply adding a touch of enchantment to your wardrobe.

bullets: Mystical Tarot Design – Perfect for fans of 90s spooky films this jumper features a stunning Empress tarot card design of a famous blonde witch on the back and chest.
Premium Cosy Materials – Crafted from a superior soft-touch cotton blend this sweatshirt provides exceptional warmth and comfort with durable stitching for long-lasting wear.
Everyday Practical Comfort – With a relaxed unisex fit this crewneck is machine washable and ideal for layering making it a versatile and low-maintenance wardrobe staple.
Vibrant Lasting Print – Our professional printing technology ensures the intricate Art Nouveau details and rich colours of the design remain sharp and vivid wash after wash.
Unique Spooky Gift – An ideal present for Halloween birthdays or any fan of magical themes this jumper is perfect for parties casual wear or cosying up for a film night.
